The paper deals with clustering, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of an oracle to answer queries is a common technique in interactive learning (cs.SI), and the information-theoretic lower bounds mentioned suggest a connection to information theory (cs.IT).
